<item>
            <title>[LU-12847] Document llapi_data_version() command and lfs-data_version.1 command</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12847</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add man page for &lt;tt&gt;llapi_data_version()&lt;/tt&gt; and the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs data_version&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; command. Clearly document whether this is only the data object version of if it includes the metadata change version.  If it does not include the metadata version, is it possible to add a flag fir the command to include the metadata version, so that userspace can determine if MDT attributes were modified.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Verify that the data_version properly covers DoM components. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
